       =000040\n|shorts2          =000040\n|socks2           =000040\n| pattern_la3 = _america1920t\n| pattern_b3 = _america1920t\n| pattern_ra3 = _america1920t\n| pattern_sh3 = _america1920t\n| pattern_so3 = _america1920t\n| leftarm3 = _america1920t\n| body3 = _america1920t\n| rightarm3 = _america1920t\n| shorts3 = _america1920t\n| socks3 = 00d8e3\n}}\n\nThe '''2019\u201320 [[Club Am\u00e9rica]] season''' is the club's 75th consecutive season in the top-flight of [[Football in Mexico|Mexican football]]. The team will participate in the [[Liga MX]], [[Campe\u00f3n de Campeones]], the [[Campeones Cup]], and the [[CONCACAF Champions League]].\n\n==Coaching staff==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:100%; width:40%;\"\n|-\n! Position\n! Name\n|-\n| Head coach\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Miguel Herrera]]\n|-\n|rowspan=3| Assistant coaches\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} \u00c1lvaro Galindo\n|-\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} [[Gilberto Adame]]\n|-\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Oscar Escobar\n|-\n| Goalkeepers coach\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Jos\u00e9 Torruco\n|-\n|rowspan=2| Fitness coaches\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Giber Becerra\n|-\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Jos\u00e9 Rangel\n|-\n| Kinesiologist\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Carlos Araujo\n|-\n|rowspan=2| Masseurs\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Jes\u00fas Zamudio\n|-\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Octavio Luna\n|-\n|rowspan=2| Doctors\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Alfonso D\u00edaz\n|-\n|align=left| {{flagicon|MEX}} Jos\u00e9 V\u00e1zquez\n|-\n| Medical assistant\n|align=left| {{flagicon|ARG}} Christian Motta\n|-\n|}\n\n==Players==\n===Squad information===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center; font-size:100%;width:80%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#FFFF94; color:#000040; text-align:center;\"| No.\n! style=\"background:#FFFF94; color:#000040; text-align:center;\"| Pos.\n! style=\"background:#FFFF94; color:#000040; text-align:center;\"| Nat.\n! style=\"background